<figureCitation box="[371,466,1400,1423]" captionStart="FIGURES 5 – 12" captionStartId="3.[151,258,1791,1813]" captionTargetBox="[204,1400,205,1756]" captionTargetId="figure@3.[185,1401,191,1770]" captionTargetPageId="3" captionText="FIGURES 5 – 12. Pelecium igneus Orsetti &amp; Lopes-Andrade sp. nov., male holotype. Aedeagus (5 – 8) 5. Dorsal view 6. Left lateral view 7. Ven tr a l v ie w 8. Right lateral view 9. Penis, right lateral view 10. Left paramere 11. Right paramere 12. Tergite IX. Scale bar: 0.5 mm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/261702/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="124">Figs 5, 7</figureCitation>
); 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[487,608,1400,1423]" pageId="1" pageNumber="124">parameres</emphasis>
